#: ../../source/manage_strategies/3. signals.md:1 trade
msgid "Operator：创建与基本配置"
msgstr "Operator: Creación y Configuración Básica"

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/3. signals.md:3 trade
msgid "Operator 是 qteasy 中策略的容器与调度器，负责在回测或实盘中按既定频率与时间点运行策略并输出统一格式的信号。"
msgstr ""
"``Operator`` es el contenedor de estrategias y el programador de qteasy. "
"Ejecuta estrategias en frecuencias y tiempos configurados en backtest o "
"trading en vivo y genera señales en un formato unificado."

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/3. signals.md:5 trade
msgid "创建 Operator"
msgstr "Crea un Operator"

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/3. signals.md:7 trade
msgid ""
"使用 ``qt.Operator()`` 创建，可传入策略列表及 ``signal_type``、``run_freq``、``run_timing``"
" 等："
msgstr ""
"Cree uno con ``qt.Operator()``, optionally passing a strategy list and "
"``signal_type``, ``run_freq``, ``run_timing`` y otros argumentos:"

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/3. signals.md:19 trade
msgid "添加策略"
msgstr "Agregar estrategias"

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/3. signals.md:21 trade
msgid ""
"**add_strategy(stg, run_freq=None, run_timing=None)**：添加单个策略，可指定该策略的 "
"``run_freq``/``run_timing``，与已有相同则归入同一 Group，否则新建 Group。"
msgstr ""
"**`⟦CÓDIGO0⟧⟦CÓDIGO1⟧⟦CÓDIGO2⟧⟦CÓDIGO3⟧⟦CÓDIGO4⟧`; se une a un grupo "
"existente si coinciden; de lo contrario, crea un nuevo grupo."

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/3. signals.md:22 trade
msgid ""
"**add_strategies(stg_list, run_freq=None, run_timing=None)**：批量添加，同样按 "
"``run_freq``/``run_timing`` 归组。"
msgstr ""
"**``add_strategies(stg_list, run_freq=None, run_timing=None)``**: Add "
"multiple strategies and group them by ``run_freq``/``run_timing`` de la "
"misma manera."

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/3. signals.md:30 trade
msgid "常用属性及含义"
msgstr "Atributos y significados comunes"

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/3. signals.md trade
msgid "属性"
msgstr "Atributo"

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/3. signals.md trade
msgid "含义"
msgstr "Significado"

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/3. signals.md trade
msgid "**signal_type**"
msgstr "**signal_type**"

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/3. signals.md trade
msgid "信号类型：`PT` 择时（目标仓位）、`PS` 择股（选股列表）、`VS` 向量信号等。"
msgstr ""
"Tipo de señal: ``PT`` position target, ``PS`` proportional signal, ``VS`` "
"señal de valor, etc."

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/3. signals.md trade
msgid "**run_freq**"
msgstr "**run_freq**"

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/3. signals.md trade
msgid "运行频率，如 `'d'` 日、`'1min'` 分钟等，与 DataType 的 freq 对应。"
msgstr ""
"Frecuencia de ejecución, por ejemplo, ``'d'`` daily or ``'1min'``; aligns "
"with ``DataTypefreq``."

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/3. signals.md trade
msgid "**run_timing**"
msgstr "**run_timing**"

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/3. signals.md trade
msgid "运行时刻，如 `'open'` 开盘、`'close'` 收盘等。"
msgstr ""
"Ejecute el tiempo, por ejemplo, ``'open'`` at open or ``'close'`` al cerrar."

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/3. signals.md trade
msgid "**groups**"
msgstr "**groups**"

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/3. signals.md trade
msgid "各 Group 信息（相同 run_freq/run_timing 的策略为一组）。"
msgstr ""
"Detalles del grupo (estrategias con el mismo ``run_freq``/``run_timing`` "
"forman un grupo)."

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/3. signals.md:39 trade
msgid "设置策略参数"
msgstr "Establecer parámetros de estrategia"

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/3. signals.md:41 trade
msgid ""
"使用 **set_parameter(stg_id, pars=None, run_freq=None, run_timing=None, ...)**"
" 为指定策略设置可调参数或归组："
msgstr ""
"Utilice **``set_parameter(stg_id, pars=None, run_freq=None, run_timing=None,"
" ...)``** para establecer parámetros ajustables o asignación de grupo para "
"una estrategia:"

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/3. signals.md:47 trade
msgid "运行前检查"
msgstr "Comprobación previa a la ejecución"

#: ../../source/manage_strategies/3. signals.md:49 trade
msgid "**is_ready()**：检查 Operator 是否已配置好策略与数据要求，可用于回测/优化前自检。"
msgstr ""
"**``is_ready()``**: Verifique si Operator está configurado con estrategias y"
" requisitos de datos; útil antes del backtest u optimización."
